tem_assets/steam/apps/702030/extras/c605508207b33d0063406f67de048f6e.mp4?t=1561077067\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/702030/extras/751226d4603b8250fec547fc75aec098.webp?t=1561077067\" width=600 height=35 /></span></li></ul>",
